text: Umm… N-no, that's not it. Should I be more assertive? Uh…
I-I said you didn't hear anything!
…Okay, fine, I'm a talking house. Satisfied?
What was I talking about? Well, it's a bit embarrassing…

I, uh, have a date for later today. 
 And yes, before you ask, there are other talking houses, 
 and they go on dates sometimes.

But I'm just so nervous! You humans have dates too, yeah? 
 Any advice you can give me?

What!? No! I'm not bringing a human to my date! 
 I'm already breaking a taboo just telling you about all this!
…You really think you can help me if I let you come with?

Fine, fine. You can tag along. I guess I could use someone in my corner. 
 But you gotta stay out of sight!
